data.description: New Construction. Excellent Opportunity for investors, Vacation Home or Primary Residence. Construction has started! Camp Swift, named for its original land owner, will consist of 6 private residences with stunning unobstructed Gulf views, summer kitchen, elevator, relaxing backyard with  private pool, outdoor fireplace 2 car garage and private roof top decks. Public beach access across the street and only minutes to 30-Avenue with shopping and restaurants, Rosemary and Alys Beach. Experience the coastal lifestyle of Inlet Beach with rental projections of $435k An additional  furniture package is available through Eiland and Rice Interiors. (See furniture options under documents)  Renderings and drawings are subject to change due to availability.
